</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Deflection shields</span><hr size=1> In my feeble attempt at pvp, i remembered i had one on when i was getting my ass kicked. I right click it, and a green aura goes around me and it says parry. I then procede to get hit by 500 damage from hammer enforcer. How are these things supposed to work? DO they even work? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/udangerousdare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>dangerousdare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#660000>(12/13/01 2:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=46.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Deflection shields</span><hr size=1> All they do is increase two of your main three AC's for a few seconds. Up to QL100 they pretty much suck. They also lock your parry skill for 5 minutes...<br>
After QL100 they are rumored to give +2000 AC for a few seconds. Although I can't confirm that and in my experience I've only ever got +100 or so.<br>
<br>
They might be nice if your near a zone and just need a little bit of a boost to make the zone line. Not really worth it in my opinion. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/utoymas69.showPublicProfile?language=EN>toymas69</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tiny Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 31<br> <font color=#660000>(12/13/01 6:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=46.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Deflection shields</span><hr size=1> I use mine when I get two or more yellow ones, or an orange+ heavy hitter. It last for some 10 seconds I think and raises the Energy and Melee AC about 100. <br>
The shield is somewhere around ql25.<br>
<br>
I've also got another type of shield, it's like a cross with thorns around - this one punch back 10 points each time anyone hit me directly (not shooting)  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I use what I can to give me those few points extra.<br>
<br>
Katzy LvL29 MA<br>
